@Kaffie: I know the feeling, I'm usually the youngest at my local pharmacy too.
And I'd guess the ones serving you might have some general idea. Even then it's not accurate. Recently I learned that Diazepam is also used for some kinds of pain management, which surprised me since before I only knew it as an anti-anxiety/antipsychotic/sleep aid.

Also, probably are robots. Try to trap them in a logic loop, see if their heads pop off. :B
